---

<section class="wws" aria-labelledby="wws-heading">
  <div class="wws-container">
    <div class="wws-label" data-animate="fade-up">Who We Serve</div>
    <h2 id="wws-heading" class="wws-heading" data-animate="fade-up">
      Built for the people who need<br />
      <em>opportunity</em> most
    </h2>
    <p class="wws-body" data-animate="fade-up" data-delay="0.1">
      Adriana's Foundation serves underserved communities, with a focus on
      Latinos, women, young adults, and single mothers who are ready to learn,
      grow, and build a better future.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .wws {
    background: var(--color-bg-light-gray);
    padding: 5rem 0;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
  }

  .wws-container {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 1.5rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .wws-label {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-terracotta);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .wws-heading {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.25rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-bg-dark);
    line-height: 1.15;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
  }

  .wws-heading em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--color-gold);
  }

  .wws-body {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin: 0;
  }
</style>
